Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:17.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:19.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He's back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:21.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:25.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's Nakao...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:26.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:27.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:30.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- He came yesterday too.\N- You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:34.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:37.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be suspicious of you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:39.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:42.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:45.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be after Kyuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:46.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.31,0:00:53.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A robot has come to our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:14.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The principal says we have to keep it a secret, at all costs, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:17.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...a crazy story like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:19.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...how would I be able to tell anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:21.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To say, "my classmate is a robot"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:31.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:34.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You... film over that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:36.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:39.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sorry. That was just a passing fancy.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:41.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just a little infatuated...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But... after I thought about it, she isn't even really my type...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:47.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Which means, I'm free too.\N- Okay. What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:49.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit filming. Don't film me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- 'Morning, Kageyama!\N- 'Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:56.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning! See you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:07.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, today, we see a scene no different than any other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:11.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:12.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- A stalker.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's following Kyuuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That would never happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:24.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:26.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:28.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If he keeps following her like this... Just look...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:29.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll find out Kyuuto's a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:33.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But... he's an otaku. He's not interested in girls, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:36.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Make Nakao give up on her.\N- How?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:39.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Figure it out!\N- What does that... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm counting on you.\N- I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm counting on you, okay?\N- No. Wait. I can't. It's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:45.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I can't. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Into the sluggish, endless everyday..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:22.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...suddenly something sparkling has appeared..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:32.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Always, we strive frantically to grasp that which shines..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:36.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...but if we hold it, for even a moment..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:41.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...we'll only return, once again, to the meaningless classroom."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sparkling"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:05.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But... we're talking about Nakao here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:11.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably should have done that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Fallen in love?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:17.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter with who... Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...going on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Ray Bradbury talks about them in his books...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Walking together at night holding hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:30.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And that night becomes once-in-a-lifetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Once-in-a-lifetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:36.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The only date you go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:38.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...a stroll at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:39.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd do something normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Go see a movie together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:53.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...then the two of us would laugh so hard we cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:04:59.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've done it before I came...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That walk with someone at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:09.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, even if the surgery fails, I'd be able to think, "that's all right."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that big a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Anything that ties you to this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...is that big a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:25.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...that nighttime walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:32.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then when I get back, it's a double date, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:54.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that holds me to this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Wow! What should we choose?\N- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:04.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hurry!\N- Hold on. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:07.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay. On the count of three...\N- Okay. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, and... that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:18.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Always we strive frantically to grasp that which shines..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:23.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...but if we hold it, for even a moment..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:29.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...we'll only return, once again, to the meaningless classroom."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:32.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...is in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:53.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Kyuuto]\NEpisode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:07:01.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,translation by sarujin\NQC by sayochama
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:09.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,GIRIGIRI FANSUBS\NNOT FOR SALE OR RENT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:15.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Filming me all the time. Is that really fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:18.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay. Then I'll film some...\N- Hey! Stupid. That's mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that? Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:31.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Yamamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yamamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:56.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. That's a pick. It's probably Yamamoto's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:57.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She plays guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:00.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...a scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A... a scale?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A scale from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:07.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The Little Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:10.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The Little Mermaid. Huh? Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:24.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you fallen in love with a human man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to meet a human man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogawa-sensei said to come right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Excuse us!\N- Did you lose your love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:41.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto is not the Little Mermaid. She's human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:44.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been human and always will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:45.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But... the scale...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:49.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a pick. It's used to play guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's made of plastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Plastic.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:57.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you need to be sure to return it to Yamamoto. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:00.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- What about the Little Mermaid?\N- She doesn't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:03.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you searched the whole world, you wouldn't find her anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's made up! A complete lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But... in books...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:10.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lies written in books.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The Little Mermaid is... a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. A lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:16.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Complete nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:20.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:24.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For what purpose... do humans write lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:32.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just don't call Yamamoto the Little Mermaid anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:35.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:42.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The Little Mermaid? Yes, I've heard of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:48.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Though she could only live in the sea she came on land.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that is extremely reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:53.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true it's stupid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:59.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think she probably knew that she was pushing herself too hard by leaving the ocean to live on land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:01.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:05.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...she was completely infatuated with that human man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Infatuated"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:11.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To be so in love that you forget things like eating and sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:19.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't live a normal life that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:22.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But... if you don't have something like that, you can't keep going, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you have that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:28.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you think you'll be able to give it your best for another day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:38.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Something I'm infatuated with? I guess, if I had to say, it'd be my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:42.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this place called "education" more than words can say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:50.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivian-chan, huh? She was a lovely girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:53.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouchou-sensei is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...infatuated with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:58.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I suppose that's what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:02.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei. Please return to your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:09.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I wrong to dispose of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I was getting rid of them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:17.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wanted to say good-bye to each of them in turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:23.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita. Are you infatuated with anything right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:25.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:36.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you infatuated with Nakao-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Sorry. I have something to do, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get home on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:48.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita is infatuated with Nakao-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:36.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You come here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:41.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Luna - Fullthrottle]\NWow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:54.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She reminds me of someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:09.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong? Why are you running? Why are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:25.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like Kyuuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- What is it?\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:42.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:46.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:49.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What kinds of things do women like to hear? What makes them happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:52.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will pay your rent."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:55.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No. That wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:14:00.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and "I will pay for your health insurance."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:02.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:11.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could kiss you, hold you tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:18.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...would your inexperienced lips soften too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:25.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You were so cool in your concert today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:26.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is private.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think that was?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:43.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:46.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:53.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Huh? What? What is it?\N- Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:56.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Just... Just...\N- What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:08.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the light of the full moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:13.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll blow out the 16th candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:18.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And after we've kissed for the 17th time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:21.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I never realize before now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:24.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother is Hajime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:26.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be our specialty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:27.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This part!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This part.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:31.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:33.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:34.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Just for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:37.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- "Our specialty..."\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Our specialty..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:44.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:46.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do it again!\N- That's enough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:50.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:53.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- What do you think you're doing?\N- Whose head do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's my head!\N- Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ow! Ow, ow, ow...\N- Don't be so selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow you'll always wear your hair this way. It's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I will! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:05.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:16.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:25.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so ugly. Do you really think Chaka is seriously going out with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear me? Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:30.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, Ugly.\N- Hey, Ugly! Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me. Why did you run, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever go near Chaka again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:40.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- You get it?\N- Give me a break. Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try messing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You think Chaka's serious about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:48.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't come to his concerts.\N- Don't ever get near him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:51.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You just stay away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:02.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:04.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme go! What d'you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:13.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:17.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:20.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A white flag means "surrender."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:27.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot injure a person who has surrendered. That is a rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:30.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- She's freaking me out!\N- We surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:35.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:51.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:56.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:02.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to just die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:09.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously thought it'd be better if I died...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:19.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...the place you can go on living?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:46.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:51.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:59.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it'd be best if I came right out and told Nakao, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:04.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch my woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"My woman"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:13.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't as if it was Kyuuto-san that I liked in the first place, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:24.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is who I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:31.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Her. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:38.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If, just if...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...you were able to go on a date or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Would that become a once-in-a-lifetime memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:49.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I say date, but I'm talking about going for a walk or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:51.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-If...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:54.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I were able to go on a w-walk with Luna-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Luna-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Luna-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:04.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- I wouldn't mind paying 30 million yen!\N- 30 million yen? You have that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:06.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How could a high school student have that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- But you said 30 million yen...\N- I'm talking about a loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:12.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,After I've graduated and gotten a steady job I'll pay you back in regular installments.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:18.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:20.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean... For going on a walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:28.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...I'll pay 40 million!\N- Okay! I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...as a final memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...you want to go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:40.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after that, you can't ever follow her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:51.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What is it? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:54.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to thank you, but I don't have anything, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:56.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. I can't. It's too important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai, you may not understand this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is how important this is to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:15.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Fukai-kun!\N- You scared me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:18.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't doing your hair like you did yesterday anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- That Hajime guy...\N- Fukai-kun, you're too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:26.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm never doing that again, ever.\N- What? Please, just one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:28.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'll do anything if you take pictures with me!\N- No. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:29.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Please?\N- No. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:52.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, isn't it? Taking this many...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:54.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- A close up on Hajime.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:03.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:04.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:12.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that Heita...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:15.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...taking pictures with a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:28.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:30.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look... Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:37.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I just look a lot like this "our specialty" idol. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:40.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she asked me to take pictures with her. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:41.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:44.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's fine. You don't have to try so hard...\N- But I know you've got the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:46.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I know you've got the wrong idea about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.56,0:22:47.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I told you didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:51.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai doesn't mean anything special to me or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:58.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No. She really doesn't. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.84,0:23:01.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:05.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:06.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.41,0:23:11.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's okay with you, would you give me your phone's email address?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:13.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So that maybe I could get in touch with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:14.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:20.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know how to...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.03,0:23:21.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Shall I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:23.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:28.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why a telephone pole?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.97,0:23:33.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I like them quite a bit, you see... telephone poles and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:36.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.75,0:23:42.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. I don't really like them that much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.25,0:23:45.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...sometimes I like the way the shape reminds me of the gates at shrines.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.32,0:23:47.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:54.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for treating me to such a lovely day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:57.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Would you like to go out for a few drinks after this? Just casually...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:23:59.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, today is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:02.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Please don't say that...\N- No. It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:03.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Please!\N- No, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.47,0:24:06.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay your rent!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.74,0:24:09.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:12.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay for your health insurance too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:17.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! No! It's not like that! It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:18.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.56,0:24:26.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for calling you out here like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.09,0:24:28.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's about that thing, right? Taking pictures with Heita...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.73,0:24:30.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.80,0:24:33.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. No. It isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.07,0:24:35.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.34,0:24:37.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.34,0:24:40.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I like idols...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.74,0:24:43.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I was hoping you wouldn't tell the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.68,0:24:48.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if people found out I'm an idol fanatic, they'd probably all be put off by it. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.25,0:24:52.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.92,0:24:55.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't think you'd understand this, Kageyama-kun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.36,0:24:58.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this is pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.36,0:25:02.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.90,0:25:03.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.93,0:25:06.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I'm the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.03,0:25:10.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there's someone I like too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.60,0:25:12.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I know that if everyone found out, they'd freak out, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.87,0:25:15.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't tell anyone the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.58,0:25:22.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kageyama-kun... You're not the way you appear, are you... You're gallant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.25,0:25:23.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.62,0:25:25.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.12,0:25:29.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the person you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.46,0:25:30.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.29,0:25:33.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...is Hajime? Just like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.13,0:25:37.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.46,0:25:40.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you like Yasu? That's great that we like different members.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.63,0:25:42.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- No... I...\N- For a second I thought you'd copied me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.77,0:25:44.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. No. I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.64,0:25:47.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Then you know about Yasu's family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.44,0:25:53.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasu's worked so hard all on his own, but his family ended up all split up...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.25,0:25:56.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The night I heard how long and hard Yasu's been working I cried!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.88,0:25:58.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe bawled?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.65,0:26:01.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- I cried too. Yeah.\N- Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.12,0:26:04.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I mean on TV Yasu's supposed to be the funny one, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.26,0:26:06.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...behind the scenes he's suffered so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.59,0:26:10.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... Unless we give him our understanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.83,0:26:12.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way to repay him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.73,0:26:15.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.14,0:26:17.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.27,0:26:20.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.78,0:26:26.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never talked about this stuff anywhere but online, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.28,0:26:32.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles do exist, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.42,0:26:36.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? They do don't they? Miracles...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.22,0:26:39.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles. Miracles do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.16,0:26:41.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.20,0:26:45.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go on a date with Nakao?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.87,0:26:46.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.17,0:26:51.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It will make Nakao happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.57,0:26:53.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.67,0:26:56.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita loves Nakao-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.38,0:26:57.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.71,0:27:00.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You are infatuated with Nakao-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.38,0:27:03.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you you've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.12,0:27:05.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Wrong?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.59,0:27:07.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I be in love with someone like Nakao?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.32,0:27:08.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.42,0:27:11.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...why do you wish to make Nakao-kun happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.13,0:27:13.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.67,0:27:20.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.30,0:27:24.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of stuff going on. Stuff you can't explain in a simple sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.91,0:27:29.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita wishes to make Nakao-kun happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.51,0:27:30.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Again? That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.68,0:27:32.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You love Nakao-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.31,0:27:37.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay. Then let's just leave it at that.\N- Heita wishes to make Nakao-kun happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.12,0:27:41.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita is infatuated with Nakao-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.76,0:27:44.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Heita loves Nakao-kun.\N- Okay! Let's just go home. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.26,0:27:46.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Heita loves Nakao-kun...\N- Okay. Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.33,0:27:50.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This part here... Make it round, very round, then pull this tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.30,0:27:53.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There. You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.94,0:28:00.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm taking a bath now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.61,0:28:04.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? He's already asleep, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.18,0:28:09.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Date. 10/22, 4 pm]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.85,0:28:12.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun... A date...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.12,0:29:17.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Kyuuto's going on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.92,0:29:22.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.46,0:29:23.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.23,0:29:28.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't be on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.60,0:29:30.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? No, a singles-mixer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.73,0:29:33.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You go on those...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.97,0:29:39.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find anyone special?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.01,0:29:42.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Special," he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.58,0:29:44.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what would you call it? Someone good?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.98,0:29:46.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Someone good"...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.21,0:29:49.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.22,0:29:50.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who complements you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.25,0:29:53.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.59,0:29:56.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.76,0:30:01.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It turns everything you thought you knew upside-down and inside-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.83,0:30:04.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just "someone who complements you" or "someone good"...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.90,0:30:07.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...nothing will turn inside-out, not in a million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.10,0:30:09.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.14,0:30:10.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.44,0:30:15.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...love won't ever begin with someone of that caliber.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.81,0:30:17.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.98,0:30:21.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a copy of those, okay? I want to check on Kyuuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.22,0:30:23.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.69,0:30:27.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,E-excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.22,0:30:28.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.96,0:30:32.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If... you did fall in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.79,0:30:33.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...and...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.26,0:30:36.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...everything you know turns upside down...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.63,0:30:40.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens to you after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.67,0:30:44.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be a different "you."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.67,0:30:49.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That... is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.50,0:31:16.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka, what you love...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.70,0:31:18.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...isn't me, is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.47,0:31:19.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.21,0:31:22.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,White dresses...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.11,0:31:24.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...shoes with slender high heels...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.55,0:31:27.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...clean-cut shoulder length hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.75,0:31:31.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...small, cute bags...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.22,0:31:35.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.12,0:31:38.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.06,0:31:41.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...the truth is, I'm not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.06,0:31:42.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.40,0:31:54.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a mermaid princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.67,0:31:56.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been forcing myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.61,0:32:00.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka, can you come to this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.05,0:32:02.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.68,0:32:05.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the places we live are different, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.10,0:32:57.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The place I can keep living...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.25,0:33:08.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.22,0:33:13.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you think you will be able to give it your best for another day?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.05,0:33:19.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I do. Probably even the day after tomorrow, and the next day, and the day after that...I'll feel that way forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.60,0:33:30.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.74,0:33:32.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.46,0:33:52.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.23,0:33:54.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.29,0:33:55.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,These too...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.70,0:34:00.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you these later, when I've developed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.00,0:34:01.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.53,0:34:03.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treasure them all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.30,0:34:07.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really enough to satisfy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.51,0:34:08.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.78,0:34:13.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I become a useless, middle-aged businessman...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.78,0:34:17.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...as long as I have this, I think I'll be able to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.99,0:34:20.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.55,0:34:23.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no helping it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.06,0:34:25.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The person I fell in love with...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.79,0:34:27.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...is 2-dimensional.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.03,0:34:32.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.67,0:34:34.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Weeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.34,0:34:42.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.98,0:34:47.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita is infatuated with Nakao-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.48,0:34:50.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I've told you it's not like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.58,0:34:54.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita wishes to make Nakao-kun happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.25,0:34:55.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.76,0:35:02.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.06,0:35:04.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...is sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.80,0:35:07.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait... it's only a little further.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.30,0:35:09.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wait... Wait! You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.60,0:35:12.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.71,0:35:16.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.01,0:35:25.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be infatuated with someone like Nakao, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.96,0:35:32.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I wanted to make him happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.89,0:35:37.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...was that I thought he was admirable, better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.80,0:35:44.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He can say, without hesitation, that he loves something that isn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.24,0:35:50.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.51,0:35:54.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...more of a coward than he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.22,0:36:01.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, I wouldn't be able to tell anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.09,0:36:07.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I think I'd be afraid to admit that love even to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.51,0:36:25.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.75,0:36:30.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.35,0:36:33.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought it might be tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.56,0:36:36.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.39,0:36:38.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.79,0:38:19.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao... said he wouldn't follow her around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.36,0:38:23.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.80,0:38:28.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You like telephone poles?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.44,0:38:31.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.20,0:38:33.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.44,0:38:35.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.71,0:38:38.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little bit moved...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.21,0:38:41.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.71,0:38:43.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I like steel towers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.82,0:38:44.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.25,0:38:46.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.32,0:38:49.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I always think people will laugh, so I never tell anyone though...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.12,0:38:51.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely understand. I'm the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.99,0:38:53.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I never tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.83,0:38:56.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people don't understand this kind of stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.40,0:38:59.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.60,0:39:00.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.27,0:39:03.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...to love something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.24,0:39:08.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about? Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.84,0:39:12.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what a person comes to love... it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.40,0:39:32.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.73,0:39:35.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there! It's n-nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.33,0:39:36.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.14,0:39:38.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.44,0:39:41.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Well... it's a paper chopstick sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.11,0:39:42.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You wrote an important note on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.91,0:39:46.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. It's sort of an old keepsake...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.05,0:39:48.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.42,0:39:52.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from a place I went to after my first paycheck, with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.42,0:39:53.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A date?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.15,0:39:55.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.52,0:39:57.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... With Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.86,0:39:59.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,With someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.73,0:40:04.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here, huh? Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.26,0:40:07.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had it all this time, never thrown it away...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.27,0:40:09.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...for it to get thrown out now...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.87,0:40:16.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't forget it, even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.21,0:40:17.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...even though it happened so long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.81,0:40:21.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm still in love with her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.55,0:40:25.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to hang on to the way I felt at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.62,0:40:31.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so nervous, worried that the girl would see right through me...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.16,0:40:34.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.06,0:40:37.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was completely fine, even with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.73,0:40:41.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.84,0:40:43.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.80,0:40:46.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. This is it! I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.34,0:40:47.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I found the chopstick sleeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.91,0:40:49.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Kubo had said...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.88,0:40:52.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...the things that tie us to this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.38,0:40:54.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...may be the smallest of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.55,0:40:58.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.15,0:41:00.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,An evening stroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.33,0:41:17.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[It hurts when I laugh.]
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.51,0:41:30.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.58,0:41:36.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Always we strive frantically to grasp that which shines..."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.76,0:41:39.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of depth to the world of idols...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.86,0:41:44.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...but if we hold it, for even a moment..."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.90,0:41:50.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...we'll only..."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.74,0:41:56.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...return once again, to the meaningless classroom."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.48,0:42:02.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.85,0:42:08.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that next week, Fujino, who has been on extended absence from school, will be returning, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.65,0:42:11.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...that desk, we'll need to clean it up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.22,0:42:12.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Fujino?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.66,0:42:14.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.03,0:42:16.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujino's been out since the beginning of the semester, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.30,0:42:18.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.93,0:42:21.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogawa-sensei is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.37,0:42:22.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujino!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.00,0:42:26.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it our best, without pushing ourselves too hard, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.71,0:42:29.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuki-chan. Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.15,0:42:41.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.19,0:42:46.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.83,0:42:51.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You can come any time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.64,0:43:04.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.24,0:43:08.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Kyuuto-san, would you mind going like this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.99,0:43:15.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Things that tie me to this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.19,0:43:19.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what a person comes to love... it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.26,0:43:24.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It turns everything you thought you knew upside-down and inside-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.44,0:43:33.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.81,0:43:36.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, and... pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.45,0:43:42.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.82,0:43:44.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.78,0:43:47.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...am in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.89,0:43:50.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Kaidan no katasumi ni...]\NIn a corner, on the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.26,0:43:52.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...suwari uzukumaru no ano hito ni...]\N...that person cowering, crouched...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.89,0:43:54.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...nani ga atta n darou]\N...I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.96,0:43:58.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Ittai nani wo mitekita n darou]\NWhat did that person see?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.30,0:44:00.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Hitogomi no naka de...]\NIn a crowd of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.27,0:44:03.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...niramiau danjou no aida ni...]\N...that man and woman glare at each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.10,0:44:05.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...nani ga okottarou]\N...I wonder what happened between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.24,0:44:12.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Ittai donna jijou ga atta n darou]\NWhat circumstances led them there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.75,0:44:21.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Itsuka boku wo yobidashita...]\NOnce, you called me outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.15,0:44:23.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...sensei ga donatteta sono scene ha...]\N...and the teacher yelled. That scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.89,0:44:25.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...donna dattarou]\N...I wonder what it looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.56,0:44:28.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Ittai boku ha nani wo shitta n darou]\NWhat on earth did I learn from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.06,0:44:31.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Itsu kara ka tsuzuiteru...]\NOn the other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.40,0:44:33.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...sensou no hate ni donna koto ga...]\N...of this war that's lasted since who knows when...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.93,0:44:35.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...matteru n darou]\N...I wonder what waits for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.87,0:44:43.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Soushite boku ni nani ga dekiru n darou]\NAnd what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.48,0:44:47.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Koto no shinsou ha nani mo...]\NThe truth of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.08,0:44:49.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...shitteiru you de shirienai...]\N...we feel like we know, but we can't learn...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.62,0:44:51.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Sore demo dou ni ka kou ni ka...]\NEven so, somehow or another...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.72,0:44:54.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...ikiteita naka ga nai]\N...It's like we were never here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.82,0:44:57.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Muda ga atteba tarirarenai]\NIt's not enough to meet with futility...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.29,0:45:00.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Demo shinjirareru mono mo sukunai]\NBut there are too few things to believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.06,0:45:04.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Tada hitotsu tashika na no ha boku no kimochi]\NThe only certain thing is my feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.83,0:45:07.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Kimi no sono koe wo kikashite yo]\NLet me hear that voice of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.73,0:45:10.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Shinjireru mono ga soko ni aru yo]\NThat's where I find something to believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.37,0:45:14.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Tada hitotsu tashika na no ha omae to no toki]\NThe only certain thing is my time with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.54,0:45:19.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Kimi ga suki]\NI love you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.25,0:45:22.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.65,0:45:26.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend has poked their nose into dangerous business.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.49,0:45:29.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Being human or not doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.82,0:45:33.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to worry for others, and being worried about by others...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.39,0:45:34.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.89,0:45:36.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.63,0:45:37.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.73,0:45:39.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A mark? On Fukai's chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.93,0:45:41.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Say you aren't. Scream it at the top of your lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.87,0:45:43.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.77,0:45:44.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fujino.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.57,0:45:46.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The same wind never blows twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.97,0:45:49.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst all of that... we live.
